short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bluejeans Redirector transparently redirects any meeting links to use Bluejeans's browser based web client.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple way to avoid the Bluejeans application. The Bluejeans redirector will let you always stay in the browser for Bluejeans meetings.
